"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Remove the needle from the skin.",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Press down lightly on the skin where the shot was given.",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Turn the person onto his or her side in case he or she vomits.",
